If you want to install an experimental mesa goto this link and download all the tar.zst files seperatly

# https://github.com/rog-ally-gaming/mesa-chimeraos/releases/tag/v24.0.1-2

Make sure they are the ONLY files in your Download folder then open terminal in the folder.(right click open terminal here)

Type this command 
# sudo pacman -U *.tar.zst
This mesa inclused AMD optimizations and extra raytracing patches, also UE5 games patches so makes Renment 2, Robocop, Lords of the fallen work.
